description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 7, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 14, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Nine Lives for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [14 Votes, Common]
